desc: Truly a labor of love. Trinkets for D is forever inspired by all things tribal and bohemian, from bohemian jewelry to tribal home decor. Each creation whether made by me or meticulously curated is intended to be unique and attract those with a love for adventure, wanderlust and individuality.

layout.text: Forever inspired by all things tribal and bohemian, each creation is either created by me or meticulously curated.  For those with a wanderlust and love of individuality.
